CurrentSelections.All.comment: Text shown when all values are selected

CurrentSelections.Of.comment: Text shown between the selected fields count {0} and total fields count {1}

Listbox.Search.comment: Action text to search in listbox

Listbox.Lock.comment: Action text to lock selections in a listbox

Listbox.Unlock.comment: Action text to unlock selections in a listbox

Listbox.ScreenReaderInstructions.value: Activating the elements below will cause content on the page to be updated
Listbox.ScreenReaderInstructions.comment: Instructions to inform screen reader users that interacting with the elements below this text will update the page content

Listbox.Search.ScreenReaderInstructions.value: The following search field filters results below as you type
Listbox.Search.ScreenReaderInstructions.comment: Instructions to inform screen reader users that the search field filters the listbox results as they type

ScreenReader.ZeroSelected.value: Value deselected. No values are selected.
ScreenReader.ZeroSelected.comment: Screen reader label for value being deselected in listbox and no values are selected.

ScreenReader.OneSelected.comment: Screen reader text for a new value being selected and only one value is currently in selection.

ScreenReader.ManySelected.comment: Screen reader text for a new value being selected and multiple values are currently in selection.

Listbox.ResultFilterLabel.comment: Describes the relationship between the search field & the results that are filtered by the input into the search field

Listbox.NoMatchesForYourTerms.value: There are no matches for your search.
Listbox.NoMatchesForYourTerms.comment: Text to indicate that there are No matches for the current search string (rnt 181026)

Listbox.ItemsOverflow.value: Currently showing a limited data set, use search to reduce the size
Listbox.ItemsOverflow.comment: Disclaimer that not all data is being shown

Listbox.Dismiss.comment: Dismiss the disclaimer that not all data is being shown

Listbox.DrillDown.comment: Tooltip for the drill-down icons on the dimension titles in charts. (pde 160210)

Menu.More.comment: Menu option to display list of additional actions to choose from (ffd 20200520)

Navigate.Back.comment: Action text to step back, as opposite to forward, a form of navigation

Navigate.Forward.comment: Action text to step forward, a form of navigation

Object.Update.Active.comment: Status text shown when a object's data is being updated

Object.Update.Cancelled.comment: Status text shown when data update has been cancelled

Selection.ClearAll.comment: Action text to clear all selections

Selection.ClearAllStates.comment: Action text to clear all states

Selection.Menu.comment: Action text to toggle selection menu

Selection.SelectAll.comment: Action text to select all selections

Selection.SelectAlternative.comment: Action text to select alternative selections

Selection.SelectExcluded.comment: Action text to select excluded selections

Selection.SelectPossible.comment: Action text to select possible selections

Visualization.LayoutError.comment: Status text shown when a visualization has layout errors

Visualization.Incomplete.comment: Status text shown when a visualization is incomplete

Visualization.Incomplete.Dimensions.comment: Text showing the number of current {0} dimensions over the total {1} number of dimensions

Visualization.Incomplete.Measures.comment: Text showing the number of current {0} measures over the total {1} number of measures

Visualization.Invalid.Dimension.comment: Status text shown when a dimension is not valid

Visualization.UnfulfilledCalculationCond.value: The calculation condition is not fulfilled
Visualization.UnfulfilledCalculationCond.comment: Message displayed when a calculation condition is not fulfilled

Visualization.Invalid.Measure.comment: Status text shown when a measure is not valid
